title: Todd Downing doesn’t want to ‘waste’ Super Bowl 2026 opportunity with Patriots after failed Jets stint

sources.name: Yahoo Sports NFL
sources.title: Todd Downing doesn’t want to ‘waste’ Super Bowl 2026 opportunity with Patriots after failed Jets stint
sources.description: A year ago, Todd Downing was part of a terrible 5-12 season with the Jets. Now, he’s in the Super Bowl as the Patriots' wide receivers coach.
